By: Rûmi
Glossary:
  - Term: Iblis
    Definition: Satan, who unlike the other angels would not prostrate
      himself before Adam.
    References:
      Title: Qur’ân
      Locus: VII 11
---
So long as thou art regarding the holy (prophets and saints) as men, know
that that view is an inheritance from Iblis.
